{"tid":1224084,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(自保)當比狗逗時，可以簡單暫停face id","createTime":"2019-06-15T01:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T01:54:00.000Z","uid":229801,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"173d3d5ba3afd7016f9e9b787a16ad88e8bbed7d","tid":1224084,"uid":229801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"暫時停用 Face ID<br />\n您可暫時避免 Face ID 解鎖您的 iPhone。<br />\n按住側邊按鈕和任一音量按鈕 2 秒。<br />\n滑桿出現後，按下側邊按鈕來立即鎖定 iPhone。<br />\niPhone 會在您長達一分鐘左右未觸碰螢幕時自動鎖定。<br />\n下次您使用密碼來解鎖 iPhone 時，便會再次啟用 Face ID。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-mo/guide/iphone/iph6d162927a/ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-mo%2Fguide%2Fiphone%2Fiph6d162927a%2Fios&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXldB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=69a5ad64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-mo/guide/iphone/iph6d162927a/ios</a>"}]}